description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Reverse Climb Cool-Down' from the channel Mike Dostal.
The workout falls under Cool-down/Cool-down.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Start at a rhythm 22 and work your way down to a rhythm 18  with Mike and Mac as you cool down. 

Max rhythm: 22, Format: Reverse Climb...
